Class BaseNewsServiceTest

  • java.lang.Object

    Tests the new children safe News Service to check. New children safe NewsService should have no articles with swearwords in their headings present. Also new service should have swear words replaced with 3 asterisks (***). Swearwords to be avoided are:
    • rupūs miltai
    • velniai rautų
    • velnias
    • velniais
